Package: wb-irrigationd
Version: @VERSION@
Section: misc
Priority: optional
Architecture: @ARCH@
Maintainer: Wiren Board Irrigation Maintainers <root@localhost>
Depends: python3 (>= 3.9), systemd, nginx
Description: Irrigation controller for Wiren Board
 Controls irrigation relays over MQTT and provides schedules, safety checks,
 a web interface and an HTTP API.
